LIST OF NEW YORK STATE PRISONS
This is a list of state prisons in New York .
The New York State Department of Corrections and Community Supervision is responsible for the care , confinement , and rehabilitation of approximately 54,700 inmates at 54 correctional facilities owned and operated by the State of New York ( as of 2014 ) .
As of 2016 New York did not contract with private prisons , according to state law .
FACILITIES Section::::Facilities .
